Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这桥感觉还真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能过得去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道 已经快坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这附近的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这桥已经不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是回去的时候还得走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的 会想想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要待多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识寄这封信的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我孙女阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约三年前从那座葛桥上掉进谷里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然命没有丢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从那以后总是呆坐着晒太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请医生各方面检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是撞着脑袋了 到现在依然原因不明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 阿花的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你很关心她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能带我去谷底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 告诉我阿花掉进谷里时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我说 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经不能反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的提亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒绝的话 就会中止对这村子的支援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 虽然不能拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话 家里人会被村里唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母如果真是为你的幸福着想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也应该能经受得起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这地步 除了逃没有别的活路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了谷 翻过山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去宽广明亮的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧 阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 那里有点脆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只有我们两个人是得不到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 受得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善一直在为我着想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是去了那边 本家会归罪于村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先过了桥再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是从绝对致命的高度掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花却自己走回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 里面却是空荡荡的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叹息说她变成“谷中归者”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谷中归者”?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个谷好像偶尔会出现这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉进谷里 虽然人是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心却被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并会在谷上架起一夜桥的夜晚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 传得太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人看见过 谷上架起只出现一个晚上的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现在占据着阿花的同样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花?被占据了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做伪葛的蔓装的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 都看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普通人很难看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于伪葛来说 还真是脆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从反方向拉的话 和文献上看到的伪葛一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳已经要下山了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着剩下的夕阳聚集过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的日照太不足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一件残酷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谷中归者”和一夜桥恐怕都不只是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都可以用伪葛来解释
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通伪葛是生活在树顶的生物 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个谷里的伪葛借助寄居生物的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体 来离开谷底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们需要更多阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在谷里得到的量不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以占据生物的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以得到阳光 积蓄力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样积聚到一定数量的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就离开寄主 集中在一起 离开山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移居去更合适的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是一夜桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约二十年前 有虫渡过一个山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候“谷中归者”会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄居的虫离开以后 不是应该恢复原状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查了一下 这个谷里没有动物的尸骸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪葛寄居尸体的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么即使离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是变回尸体而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 阿花总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说上次看到一夜桥是我爷爷出生那年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷今年60岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法不让它离开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奢望变回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能活久一点就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活得久点就是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法能把那虫驱除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样做的话十有八九会当场死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这孩子这样活下去会幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不这样铤而走险也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果三年前的那个时候还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜桥出现之后就会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会出现吗 什么时候出现压根不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花能恢复原状的话 还能谈个好亲事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然不是以前的她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她还是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能像物品一样使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 明天就能把桥补好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人住这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人虽然在这个村里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被村子流放了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人和我断绝关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想自己出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 虽然想过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阿花还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花不在了的话 大概那时候我就会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于断掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你走了过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近谁也没用这桥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 大家都正忙于工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微得花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那个虫师藏起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是“谷中归者”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这附近还有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好好活着的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是阿花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了而已是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过不要接近阿花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点啊 阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻出了黑色的线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说善 你也离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕今晚 会出现一夜桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里登上去的话 应该能渡过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近已经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有无数你看不到的积攒着力量的伪葛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜半之前决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过这次机会 就不知道何时才能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有迷恋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这座桥上回头 就会掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能前进了 在这里面有阿花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 阿花三年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这三年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是期待着阿花会活回来才坚持下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看到她那样子很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在这样 更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法伪装 无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 我不清楚他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个谷上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再架起只出现一夜的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼中
